    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... my blood sugar is already pretty low right now because i barely ate. if i take the basal i'm almost certain i'll wake up in a dangerous state. its just one night, how much harm can it really do to skip a single dose if my glucose is already trending down? it seems more logical to just skip it than to risk a crash.",
